Fix Meson configuration: configuration fails under Meson
1.9.2 when the list gl_reqs is empty.

This is fixed by passing the actual list of strings to pkg.generate(),
instead of the aggregated string.

https://github.com/anholt/libepoxy/pull/313
--- src/meson.build.orig	2022-02-17 06:56:12.000000000 -0600
+++ src/meson.build	2026-04-10 13:18:32.000000000 -0500
@@ -117,5 +117,5 @@
     'epoxy_has_wgl=@0@'.format(epoxy_has_wgl),
   ],
   filebase: 'epoxy',
-  requires_private: ' '.join(gl_reqs),
+  requires_private: gl_reqs,
 )
